data.description: Great location out of the busy city center, yet close to parks and shopping! This Jackson Estate Home has new landscaping and a back patio with a wood fenced yard to enjoy your privacy. 3 Bedrooms with 2.5 baths, granite kitchen counters, remodeled bathroom, a laundry room and large pantry as well as updated laminate flooring, wood flooring and more!!! There's extra flooring to replace the carpet in the living room if you wanted too!
